Title:
Search returns "No results found" for existing products when searching "Laptop"

Summary:
When the user searches for the keyword "Laptop", the system displays the message "No results found" even though products containing the word "Laptop" exist in the database.

Environment:
Chrome 145.0.7632.160 (64-bit)
Windows 10

Severity: Major
Priority: High (P0)

Steps to Reproduce:

Open homepage

Click on the search bar

Type "Laptop"

Press Enter

Expected Result:
The system should display all products containing the word "Laptop".

Actual Result:
The system displays the message "No results found".

